\c 16
\s Impendulo kaJobe. Usola ngokuphathwa kwakhe nguNkulunkulu
\p
\v 1 Wasephendula uJobe wathi:
\p
\v 2 Ngizwile izinto ezinengi ezinje\x + 12.3.\x*; lingabaduduzi abakhathazayo lina lonke\x + 13.4.\x*.
\v 3 Kuzakuba lesiphetho yini emazwini angumoya? Kumbe kuyini okulicunulayo ukuthi liphendule\x + 6.25.\x*?
\v 4 Lami bengingakhuluma njengani uba umphefumulo wenu ubusendaweni yomphefumulo wami; bengingabuthelela amazwi phezu kwenu, ngilinikinele ikhanda lami\x + Jer. 18.16. Mat. 27.39. 2 Kho. 19.21.\x*.
\v 5 Bengingaliqinisa ngomlomo wami, lokunyikinyeka kwendebe zami bekungadedisa\x + 16.6.\x* \add ubuhlungu benu\add*.
\v 6 Uba ngikhuluma, ubuhlungu bami kabudedi; uba ngiyekela, kuyini okusuka kimi?
\v 7 Kodwa khathesi ungidinisile yena, wena uchithile yonke inhlangano yami\x + 15.34. 1.15-19.\x*.
\v 8 Ungitshwabhanisile\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x*, kube yibufakazi\x + 10.17.\x*, lokucaka kwami\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x* kungivukele\x + Hlab. 109.24.\x*, kuyafakaza ebusweni bami.
\p
\v 9 Ulaka lwakhe luya\add ngi\add*dwengula\x + 10.16. 18.4. Hos. 6.1. Amos 1.11.\x*, njalo uyangizonda\x + 30.21. Gen. 27.41.\x*; ungigedlela amazinyo akhe\x + Hlab. 35.16. 37.12. Hlab. 112.10. Lilo 2.16.\x*; isitha sami singicijisela amehlo aso\x + Hlab. 7.12.\x*.
\v 10 Bangikhamisela umlomo wabo\x + 29.23. Hlab. 22.13. Isa. 5.14.\x*, bangiwakala esihlathini ngokuyangisa\x + Lilo 3.30. Isa. 50.6. 1 Kho. 22.24.\x*, bengihlanganyela ndawonye.
\v 11 UNkulunkulu unginikele kokhohlakeleyo\x + 19.18.\x*, wangiphosela ezandleni zababi\x + Nani 22.32.\x*.
\v 12 Ngangonwabile, kodwa wangichoboza\x + Isa. 24.19.\x*, wangidumela ngentamo, wangiphahlaza\x + Jer. 23.29.\x*, wangimisa ngaba yinto yakhe yokunenjwa\x + 7.20. Lilo 3.12.\x*.
\v 13 Abatshoki bakhe bangigombolozela\x + 6.4. Jer. 50.29.\x*; uqhekeze izinso zami, engayekeli, wachithela emhlabathini inyongo yami\x + Lilo 2.11.\x*.
\v 14 Wangivodloza ngokuvodlovodloza\f + \fk ngokuvodlovodloza: \fl Heb. \fq ngokufohla phezu kokufohla.\f*, wagijimela kimi njengeqhawe\x + 30.14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Ngathunga isaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x* phezu kwesikhumba sami\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x*, ngathukuza uphondo lwami othulini\x + Hlab. 75.10.\x*.
\v 16 Ubuso bami bubomvu ngokukhala\x + Lilo 1.20. 2.11.\x*, lenkotsheni zami kulethunzi lokufa\x + 3.5.\x*,
\v 17 lanxa kungekho isihluku ezandleni zami, lomkhuleko wami uhlanzekile\x + Isa. 53.9.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Mhlaba, ungaligqibeli igazi lami\x + Isa. 26.21. Hez. 24.7.\x*, lokukhala kwami kakungabi landawo\x + Gen. 4.10.\x*.
\v 19 Lakhathesi, khangelani, ubufakazi bami busemazulwini, lomfakazi wami usezindaweni eziphakemeyo\x + Hlab. 89.37.\x*.
\v 20 Abangane bami bayangiklolodela; ilihlo lami liyathonta kuNkulunkulu.
\v 21 Kungathi kungaba khona ongamlamulela umuntu kuNkulunkulu, njengendodana yomuntu kumngane wayo\x + 9.33.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba iminyaka emilutshwana izafika, njalo ngizahamba \add nge\add*ndlela engingayikubuya \add ngayo\add*.
